      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Chemical Engineering              : Fluid properties; dimensional analysis; drag; packed/fluidized beds; macroscopic energy balances, Bernoulli's equation and linear momentum theorem; flowmeters, pipeline systems, non-Newtonian fluids, microscopic balances leading to continuity and Navier-Stokes equations; boundary layer approximation; turbulence. Laboratory exercises.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
